title: Associated Press warns that AP Stylebook data breach led to phishing attack
description: The Associated Press is warning of a data breach impacting AP Stylebook customers where the attackers used the stolen data to conduct targeted phishing attacks. [...]

title: 'Evil Telegram' Android apps on Google Play infected 60K with spyware
description: Several malicious Telegram clones for Android on Google Play were installed over 60,000 times, infecting people with spyware that steals user messages, contacts lists, and other data. [...]
